title: Trains and Rain
description:
Welcome to episode 18 of Sleep and Relax ASMR! Today's episode features some lovely sounds of trains passing by during a rainy day. Great audio for trying to fall asleep or concentrate with some background noise.

Get in touch with the show: SleepandRelaxASMR@Gmail.com. 

Thanks to Klankbeeld and Sclolex (freesound.org) for some of the great audio used this episode!
